snippet.textDisplay: I recently visited Jaipur, Rajashthan and the vibe which I noticed there in comparison to Haryana was too good the culture the people's the things to see the vehicle the places the heritage building hotel and parks were like amazing and all my trip was worth it the main thing I loved was science center and amber fort there the thing they say that padharo mare desh that is a nice gesture to welcome a traveller or one who has came first time there the view in the way is also good and met the foreigners there and talked to them about jaipur and they were very happy to come here and according to me one must go there atleast once with friends and family its a best place
